s/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2553fa93a951057835556e380ca00c1768b2570b","tid":359833,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ive engine 有dd 後悔今年冇報水泡, 諗住下年報返<br />\n不過讀完水泡同就咁hd 出黎都唔打算做返本科<br />\n以家好彩搵到間engine 公司做下文職過下日晨就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打辛苦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽人講n展chur到爆<br />\n你捱到已經好厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主共勉之<br />\n每科都有每科既壓力既<br />\n我個科engine 算係咁 唔算真係chur 到叫生叫死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3b149aa0c19bf668ea71e96ad802081da11cff","tid":359833,"uid":6101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"可以試下報埋city u BSc creative media <br />\n祝好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5830e201156b36122521e23dfe2aedd34fd65a60","tid":359833,"uid":133281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"小弟 asso過來人 升左上去就grad <br />\n唔清楚IVE hd架構係點 <br />\n我地戈邊通常year one已經會報一次non ju<br />\n衰左y2可以再報 <br />\n<br />\n唔好灰心 唔知係hd 黎講3.3算唔算高...<br />\n係我地呢邊IT asso 你既gpa至少會有interview <br />\n記住搵熟既lecturer幫你寫reference letter , <br />\napply戈陣upload埋比大學戈邊<br />\nInterview溫下書 做個正常人(好緊要 IT好多人唔正常）就掂 <br />\n相信自己 捱埋佢"},{"pid":"d4219bd48944e110a08bd245c7e3d593f71bda0f","tid":359833,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"有冇過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397f9c8f6c5cfec6c310191b49255a26dea02696","tid":359833,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:05:36.000Z","msg":"ive 邊科it hd先<br />\n呢個分都其實都應該入到讀CU board base CS CE advanced standing????<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之前cg3.29入cu engi